==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-æsɪt|-æsɪt]]

===Adjective===
'''tacit'''
# Done or made in silence; implied, but not expressed; silent; as, tacit consent is consent by silence, or by not interposing an objection.
# Not derived from formal principles of reasoning; In logic, based on induction rather than deduction.


